title: City Inside/Out debates the City Council District 6 race between Dan Strauss, Heidi Wills
description:
Former Seattle City Councilmember Heidi Wills is hoping to make a return to Seattle politics. Will voters in Northwest Seattle and Ballard give her another chance or favor a current City Council policy advisor, Dan Strauss?

Guests:  
Dan Strauss, Seattle City Council Candidate (District 6)
Heidi Wills, Seattle City Council Candidate (District 6)
